OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,FThree victims of a "disgusting"
OL,7,Fpaedophile have waived their right to
OL,8,Fanonymity to speak out about the
OL,9,Ftrauma they suffered after their
OL,10,Fabuser was jailed for 31 years.
OL,12,FJoanna Hobbs, Megan O'Brien, Victoria
OL,13,FBunch - and a fourth woman who has not
OL,14,Fbeen named - were all attacked by Paul
OL,15,FMundy as children.
OL,17,FMundy, now 71, of Market Place in
OL,18,FBawtry, Doncaster, was convicted of 24
OL,19,Fcounts of rape and sexual assault
OL,20,Fafter a trial at Sheffield Crown Court.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
