PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,FHe was jailed for 31 years.
OL,8,F'Justice has been served'
OL,10,FMs Hobbs was just five years old when
OL,11,FMundy - her stepfather - started to
OL,12,Fabuse her.
OL,14,FIn a statement she said left her
OL,15,F"frozen in fear".
OL,17,F"Being abused made me feel I was to
OL,18,Fgive my body freely - it was what I
OL,19,Fbelieved was normal," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,F"As a child it was scary and I
OL,7,Fdetached during the abuse, frozen in
OL,8,Ffear, I felt unsafe and vulnerable -
OL,9,Fsomething to be used like an object,
OL,10,Fnot something to be loved.
OL,12,F"I have carried this trauma with me
OL,13,Ffor many years. Small things will
OL,14,Fremind me of my childhood and take me
OL,15,Fback - songs from my childhood, the
OL,16,Fsmell of Lenor fabric conditioner,
OL,17,Fcoffee, mushrooms and corn on the cob.
OL,19,F"Everyday things that will remind me,
OL,20,FI can never ever escape these
OL,21,Fmemories."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,FShe said it was "empowering" to speak
OL,7,Fout about what had happened following
OL,8,FMundy's sentencing.
OL,10,F"Hearing other women's statements
OL,11,Fduring this court process and fully
OL,12,Funderstanding the extent of his abuse
OL,13,Fand repeated patterns has been
OL,14,Fheartbreaking," she added
OL,16,F"I am truly grateful that finally
OL,17,Fjustice has been served, and no more
OL,18,Fyoung girls will be at the hands of
OL,19,Fthis disgusting, vile, lying,
OL,20,Fdeceitful paedophile."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
