PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,F'You do not get to write my ending'
OL,8,FMs O'Brien was Mundy's step-
OL,9,Fgranddaughter. Her abuse began when
OL,10,Fshe was in primary school.
OL,12,FIn her statement she said it had "long-
OL,13,Flasting effects on my mental health,
OL,14,Fmy education, and my relationships".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,FAddressing Mundy directly she said:
OL,7,F"That betrayal is something I carry
OL,8,Fevery day. It changed the way I see
OL,9,Fpeople, the way I interpret love, and
OL,10,Fthe way I understand my own worth.
OL,11,FWhat you did to me took away my sense
OL,12,Fof safety and trust when I was most
OL,13,Fvulnerable.
OL,15,F"Having been subjected to your
OL,16,Ftormented ideologies from such a young
OL,17,Fage affected the most influential time
OL,18,Fof my cognitive development.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,F"Through adolescence into adulthood, I
OL,7,Fwas shaped to believe that love comes
OL,8,Fin one form: abuse. I was groomed into
OL,9,Fbelieving that those around me could
OL,10,Fonly ever value me for my body."
OL,12,FShe added that she was learning that
OL,13,Fher experience did "not have to
OL,14,Fdefine" her future.
OL,16,F"I have taught myself to speak, to
OL,17,Ftake up space, and to recognise my own
OL,18,Fvalue beyond what was forced onto me,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,F"You may have shaped part of my story,
OL,7,Fbut you do not get to write the
OL,8,Fending. I made myself strong. I made
OL,9,Fmyself loud. And I am still becoming
OL,10,Fsomeone you will never have control
OL,11,Fover again."
OL,13,F'You left me feeling embarrassed and
OL,14,Fashamed'
OL,16,FMs Bunch was a teenager when she was
OL,17,Fassaulted by Mundy.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,FShe said it left her feeling
OL,7,F"embarrassed and ashamed" and
OL,8,Fcontinues to impact her day-to-day
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,F"I tried to hide it for years and push
OL,12,Fit to the back of my mind in order to
OL,13,Fforget about it," she said. "However,
OL,14,Fthat didn't completely happen. It
OL,15,Fturns out that if anyone was to walk
OL,16,Finto my room to wake me up, I am up
OL,17,Finstantly without the need to even say
OL,18,Fmy name.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,F"When I got married it would rear its
OL,7,Fugly head in the morning when my
OL,8,Fhusband would roll over to try and
OL,9,Fcuddle me. I couldn't even let him hug
OL,10,Fme... I can never let my guard down.
OL,11,FIt is absolutely exhausting being
OL,12,Faware of everyone, I can never settle,
OL,13,Fnor have any fun."
OL,15,F'We are here to listen'
OL,17,FDet Con Jamie Bennett, of South
OL,18,FYorkshire Police, praised the
OL,19,F"courage" of Mundy's victims.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,FHe added: "The road to justice has
OL,7,Fbeen complex and, even in the face of
OL,8,Fa trial, all four victims continued to
OL,9,Fshow immense bravery resulting in two
OL,10,Fdozen convictions and a significant
OL,11,Fprison sentence for Mundy.
OL,13,F"The appalling and long-standing
OL,14,Fimpact of Mundy's crimes cannot be
OL,15,Foverstated but I hope the passing of
OL,16,Fthis sentence allows the four women to
OL,17,Frebuild their lives after such a
OL,18,Fhorrific ordeal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
