PN,36512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779462670
OL,3,CPeodophile's vicitms waive anonymity
OL,4,Cto speak out on abuse
OL,6,F"Mundy's crimes were non-recent and I
OL,7,Freally want to stress that it does not
OL,8,Fmatter when offences took place. If
OL,9,Fyou have been a victim of sexual abuse
OL,10,Fin the past, please report it to us.
OL,12,F"We are here to listen, and it really
OL,13,Fis never too late to report a sexual
OL,14,Foffence."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
